From 5c2bc5972a969a8d641a586935b1f506b6d4a3bd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: RivonClaw CI <ci@rivonclaw.com>
Date: Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:26:21 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 1/8] vendor(openclaw): add browser lifecycle hooks for plugin
 integration

Why:
- RivonClaw needs to track browser session lifecycle (start/stop) to persist session state (cookies) across restarts
- RivonClaw needs before/after action hooks for future extensibility (auth injection, captcha solving, page preparation)
- Existing before_tool_call/after_tool_call hooks lack browser-specific context and proper timing semantics

Removal:
- When OpenClaw adds native browser lifecycle hooks upstream
- Track: propose as upstream PR after proving the design in RivonClaw

Tests:
- extensions/browser-profiles-tools/src/browser-lifecycle-hooks.test.ts
